g.text: SHEET: Name of the page (e.g. "Supply Circuit")
BOARD: Name of the board (e.g. "THT Prototype")
PROJECT: Name of the project (e.g. "Brushless Controller")
PROJECT_DIRPATH: Absolute path to the project directory (e.g. "/home/me")
PROJECT_BASENAME: Basename of the project file (e.g. "MyProject")
PROJECT_FILENAME: Filename of the project file (e.g. "MyProject.lpp")
PROJECT_FILEPATH: Absolute path to the project file (e.g. "/home/me/MyProject.lpp")
AUTHOR: Name of the author (e.g. "Homer Simpson")
VERSION: Version number of the project (e.g. "v1.2")
PAGE_X_OF_Y: Convenience attribute which always contains "Page {{PAGE}} of {{PAGES}}"
